cventers-qpsmtpd-plugins

filter/dkimsign - My spin of a Mail::DKIM-based signature plugin

filter/header_whitelist - Clean up headers generated by backend mail
generators

queue/smtp-forward - Stock qpsmtpd smtp-forward extended with Postfix XCLIENT
support. Note that the copyright on this belongs to the qpsmtpd developers;
I've only extended it and intend on submitting these changes upstream.

config/header_whitelist - An example header whitelist configuration

